t know what to say.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a heartfelt statement\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stuff like this happens way more often than we would all like.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stuff\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not expect it to happen in a little town like Southport.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\", \"score\": 0.9996852405224038, \"rank\": 0.00031485853459645207, \"text\": \"Southport\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little town\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The whole thing is just terrible; it's obviously tragic for the town and everybody involved, but for those directly affected, it's simply horrific.\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The whole thing\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"the town\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your first thoughts are always with the families who have tragically lost loved ones or those who will have to live with this for the rest of their lives.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your first thoughts\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the families\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"loved ones\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just not fair.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When one of you g